==Greek==
===Etymology===
Mycenaean [[𐀂𐀦]] (''i-qo''), from Proto-Indo-European ''*eḱwos'', possibly derived from ''*ōḱu-'' "swift".  Unexplained is ''ἱ'' (hi) for ''*ἐ'' (*e).  Cognates include Latin [[equus]].  

